   <body>
      <p>A program is a collection of proposed and authorized projects.</p>
      <p>A program provides a comprehensive view of project requirements and available funds.</p>
      <p>The <uicontrol>Program</uicontrol> form enables you to: <ul>
            <li>Add multiple planned projects  to a program</li>
            <li>Group projects under a program and assign funds</li>
            <li>View funds that are available, remaining, andrequired</li>
            <li>View details of each fund category and fund source</li>
            <li>View the forecast of the program over the program period</li>
            <li> Perform what-if analysis by creating multiple program scenarios and selecting the best scenario for approval</li>
            <li>Performwhat-if analysisusing fund views</li>
            <li>Create snapshots for comparison</li>
            <li>Approve projects </li>
            <li>Manage program revisions</li>
            <li>Generate reports</li>
         </ul>
      </p>
